metadata.description: Airdropped items can be unlocked on https://unlock-bayc.com. Baby Ape Yacht Club is a collection of 1,000 unique Baby Ape NFTs. BAYC was airdropped as an event with the total trading volume of BAYC reaching 1,000,000 ETH on OpenSea. Airdropped items are locked and can be traded after unlocking.
